<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">近日，2023年第二十届全国大学生信息安全与对抗技术竞赛（简称“ISCC2023”）个人挑战赛结果揭晓。江西软件职业技术大学网络工程学院2021级信息安全技术应用（渗透测试）专业C2021113班谢肾龙和欧阳坤同学经过25天的激烈比拼，奋勇拼搏、勇创佳绩，夺得全国赛区一等奖。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-09%2015%3A03%3A19%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png?Expires=2001654199&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=s4OqUELq8xz%2FX0Fr81IaSsDg1lA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="248" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-09%2015%3A03%3A33%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.png?Expires=2001654213&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Ym7JKBhSz43UJUSyhLLUmyCKpSY%3D" alt="" width="650" height="172" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">ISCC2023竞赛个人挑战赛是一项全国性的大型比赛，参赛者均来自于各大高校，包括211、985院校。竞赛于2023年5月1日开赛，赛程持续25天，吸引了全国1000多所院校、近8000名选手注册参赛。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江西软件职业技术大学作为全国首个软件大学，始终坚持职业教育属性、“为党育人、为国育才”的目标，落实立德树人的任务，始终围绕信息技术前沿设置专业。长期以来，学校一直高度重视学生专业竞技能力及专业实践能力的培养，积极组织广大学生广泛参与各类学科竞赛及学术实践活动，并着重培养学生的创新创业能力。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-09%2015%3A04%3A20%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png?Expires=2001654260&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=7x13yS65UEw8WusKYZT6BYJHiRk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">信息安全技术应用（渗透测试）专业由学校和南昌江来科技有限公司校企合作共同进行人才培养，江来科技派遣网络安全工程师全程参与专业课程教学和实验实训，采用项目化教学来提高学生专业技能和竞赛水平，通过2年来的实践，学生的专业技能得到了明显提高，此次成绩的取得也是我校坚定不移地走产教融合校企合作的办学之路成果的体现。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">ISCC2023竞赛由中国兵工学会、中国兵工学会信息安全与对抗专业委员会主办，北京理工大学信息系统及安全对抗实验中心（工信部）、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">北京理工大学信息安全与对抗技术研究所承办。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">2023年3月22日，全国大学生信息安全与对抗技术竞赛(ISCC)入选全国普通高校大学生竞赛目录。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">ISCC宗旨为全面贯彻国家关于网络空间安全和信息化工作的重要精神，提升信息安全意识，普及信息安全知识，实践信息安全技术，共创信息安全环境，发现信息安全人才。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-09%2015%3A04%3A43%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png?Expires=2001654283&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=5o5zm394KvBN%2Bm8hKQdyR9e1rpc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="100" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p><br/></p>